questions.question:
For the following code, indicate the output if
a. static scope rules
b. dynamic scope rules
are used

var a, b : integer;
procedure P;
  a := 5;
  b := 10;
end {P};
procedure Q;
  var a : integer;
  begin
    a := 2;
    b := 3;
    P;
  end {Q};
begin
  a := 1;
  b := 2;
  Q;
  Write (a = ', a, ' b = ', b);
end

A. Static: a=5, b=10; Dynamic: a=1, b=10
B. Static: a=5, b=10; Dynamic: a=5, b=10
C. Static: a=1, b=10; Dynamic: a=1, b=10
D. Static: a=5, b=10; Dynamic: a=2, b=10

